   RUN DAILY
   RELEASE ADD(ZSDPRI05_PRICEBOOK_DOWNLOAD)
ENDJOB

SAP_JOB ZSDPRI05_PRICEBOOK_DOWNLOAD
   AGENT CYBB_BFP030
   SAPJOBNAME ZSDPRI05_PRICEBOOK_DOWNLOAD
   SAPJOBCLASS C
   STARTMODE ASAP
   ABAPNAME ZSDPRI05
   VARIANT PRCBK_DWNLOAD
   STEPUSER SAPADM
   LANGUAGE E
   PRINTDEST CP21
   PRINTCOPIES 001
