   LINES 65
   COLUMNS 80
   BANNER D
   RECIPIENT sapadm
   ARCMODE PRINT
   RUN WEEKDAYS
   RELEASE ADD(LIE.!ESPAPPL)
ENDJOB

JOB LIE.!ESPAPPL LINK PROCESS
   RUN DAILY
   DUEOUT EXEC NOW PLUS 6 HOURS
